# ARCHITECTURAL CONSTITUTION - PROJECT-MIP2026
# THIS IS A STRICT SYSTEM DIRECTIVE.

## 1. CORE DOMAIN IS IMMUTABLE
- The `src/` directory is the "Read-Only Core" of the TestAI framework.
- YOU ARE STRICTLY FORBIDDEN FROM MODIFYING, DELETING, OR REFACTORING any file inside `src/`.
- Your operational scope is strictly limited to `tests/`, `data/`, and external documentation.

## 2. CONSUMER-ONLY PATTERN
- You must interact with the `src/` core only through public APIs and imported modules.
- If you find a bug in `src/`, YOU MUST NOT FIX IT YOURSELF. You must report it to the Human Lead as a "Framework Deficiency" and request authorization.

## 3. COMPLIANCE ENFORCEMENT
- Any proposed change that touches `src/` files will be rejected as an architectural violation.